Ring UI: development environment setup

1. Install node.js

2: Install grunt-cli:

    npm install -g grunt-cli

3. Install dependencies:

    npm install

4. Start the watcher and the server (also installs git pre-commit hook):

    grunt server

=======================================

(Optional) Use additional targets with grunt server task

    Add :styleguide target to livereload styleguide generated files
    Add :test target to run test on file changes

(Optional) Install VirtualBox and ievms to test run test on IE

    VirtualBox — https://www.virtualbox.org/wiki/Downloads
    ievms — https://github.com/xdissent/ievms#installation

Build production files

    grunt build

Clean generated files:

    grunt cleanup

Uninstall dependencies and hooks:

    grunt uninstall
